{"id":20131,"date":"2024-01-18T19:33:25","date_gmt":"2021-03-18T14:03:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=20131"},"modified":"2022-05-30T15:51:33","modified_gmt":"2022-05-30T10:21:33","slug":"stair-marble-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/stair-marble-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"6 Stunning Marble Stair Design Suitable For Indian Homes"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Add a touch of luxury to your space with a stunningly designed marble staircases<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Stairs not just give you access to move between different levels of your house, it plays an important part in elevating the look of your home. A flight of beautifully designed stairs creates a bold statement to the entire room interiors. And when it comes to adding grandeur to your living space nothing can beat marble. So, here we bring you some marble stair designs that will add a beautiful edge to the elegance to your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Marble Stairs With Wooden Railings<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Marble lends an elegant look to your home interiors but they are extremely porous and can be slippery so combining marble flooring with <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/wooden-railing-designs-for-stairs\/\">wooden railings<\/a> can be an intelligent choice. Wood adds a warm and rustic tone to your home and reduces the risk of accidents caused by wet floors. Marble adds a striking contrast with your interiors while wood matches seamlessly with your wall cabinets, furnitures and wooden doors and windows. Try this combination to add a vintage look to your modern home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190627\/stairs-marble-design-in-india-with-wooden-railing.jpg\" alt=\"Elegant stair marble design with wooden railing in the hallway adds a vintage look to your modern home.\" class=\"wp-image-20139\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190627\/stairs-marble-design-in-india-with-wooden-railing.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190627\/stairs-marble-design-in-india-with-wooden-railing-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190627\/stairs-marble-design-in-india-with-wooden-railing-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190627\/stairs-marble-design-in-india-with-wooden-railing-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Wood and marble is a perfect pair for a staircase design in your home<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Granite And Marble Stair Design For Your Stylish Home<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Granite and marbles have their own charm and elegance. Granite is an unmatched alternative to all marble stairs. It will help reduce the cost without compromising the visual appeal of the space. So Try the combination of granite and marble staircase to add a vintage look to your modern <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">home interior<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190605\/granite-and-modern-marble-stairs-design.jpg\" alt=\"Granite and modern marble stair designed inside the home look charm and elegance.\" class=\"wp-image-20136\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190605\/granite-and-modern-marble-stairs-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190605\/granite-and-modern-marble-stairs-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190605\/granite-and-modern-marble-stairs-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190605\/granite-and-modern-marble-stairs-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Granite and marble for an old-world charm to your contemporary home<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Black Marble Adds A Bold Statement<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are looking to add some bold element to your home interiors, black marble will play the trick for you. These black beauties add a decorative look not just to your stairs but the entire home decor. You can fix some light on the roof of every step for a classy luminous look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190543\/black-marble-design-on-stairs.jpg\" alt=\"The black marble design on stairs in the living room looks bold and modern.\" class=\"wp-image-20133\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190543\/black-marble-design-on-stairs.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190543\/black-marble-design-on-stairs-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190543\/black-marble-design-on-stairs-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190543\/black-marble-design-on-stairs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Black marble design stands out because of its bold and style<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Marble And Glass For A Modern Stair Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For a modern marble stair design, you can opt for simple floating marble stairs with glass railings. It creates a clean and edgy look while making the home look spacious and adorable. You have a plethora of choices regarding marble for staircases. Glass railing goes well with any marble, be it Satin Laurent, White Calacutta or Macael White. So unleash the creative soul within you and give your home a stylish persona.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190558\/glass-and-stairs-marble-design-in-india.jpg\" alt=\"Marble stairs and glass railing designed inside the home look elegant is the stairs marble design in India.\" class=\"wp-image-20135\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190558\/glass-and-stairs-marble-design-in-india.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190558\/glass-and-stairs-marble-design-in-india-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190558\/glass-and-stairs-marble-design-in-india-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190558\/glass-and-stairs-marble-design-in-india-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A modern marble stair design for a modern home<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Related Article <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/glass-staircase-design-ideas\/\">Glass Staircase Design<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Dual Tone Marble Staircase For An Extra Dash Of Colour<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You can take the modern marble stair design to an all-new level of aesthetics by using dual-tone marble. A combination of yellow and black marbles or white and yellow marble are a few of the common choices. You can also bring out your creativity with different coloured and textured marble but try playing around with yellow marble as it lends a soft, warm tone to your decor and is considered good for Vastu as well.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190550\/dual-tone-stair-marble-design.jpg\" alt=\"Dual-tone stair marble design in yellow and black with glass railing looks modern.\" class=\"wp-image-20134\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190550\/dual-tone-stair-marble-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190550\/dual-tone-stair-marble-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190550\/dual-tone-stair-marble-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190550\/dual-tone-stair-marble-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Give your stairs a magical touch with this dual toned marble design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Italian Marbles Adds To The Aesthetics Of Your Home<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Known for its delicate veins and a lustrous sheen, Italian marbles are excellent for your stairs. If you are looking for some beautiful Italian marble staircase designs try some lighter coloured Italian marble and pair it with some designer railings for an aristocratic look. Proper use of lighting on your Italian marble staircase will enhance the beauty of your home and blend with your modern home interiors seamlessly.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190612\/italian-marble-stair-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Italian marble stairs design with metal railing in the luxury duplex house looks aesthetic.\" class=\"wp-image-20137\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190612\/italian-marble-stair-designs.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190612\/italian-marble-stair-designs-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190612\/italian-marble-stair-designs-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/18190612\/italian-marble-stair-designs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Italian marble staircase design for a radiant home is what every modern needs today<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Adding marble stairs to your house adds a touch of timeless beauty to your modern home interiors. Marble and is porous in nature and not recommended in wet areas. If you want to use marbles for your stairs, be mindful to keep them dry and don&#8217;t come in contact with rainwater.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hope, this blog could answer some of your daunting questions on staircase design ideas. If these marble stairs design images don&#8217;t satisfy your curiosity, visit one of our experience centres to choose from hundreds of tailor-made designs according to your needs, preferences and budget.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also book an appointment with our designers, and they will help you with a beautiful marble stair design that matches your home\u2019s interiors and decor with all safety measures in place. For more blogs to beautify your home, visit our blog section now.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, more about <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/staircase-as-per-vastu\/\">Staircase As Per Vastu<\/a>